OL,6,FA mural of Huw Edwards has been
OL,7,Fremoved from his home village just
OL,8,Foutside Llanelli.
OL,10,FThe former BBC presenter pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt on Wednesday to three counts of
OL,13,Fmaking indecent images of children.
OL,15,FThe portrait, which was part of a
OL,16,Flarger mural, was on the underpass in
OL,17,Fthe village of Llangennech, where
OL,18,FEdwards grew up.
