OL,6,FIt was first unveiled in 2023 after
OL,7,Ftaking a year to paint by artist Steve
OL,8,FJenkins.
OL,10,FHowever, Mr Jenkins has confirmed that
OL,11,Fthe portrait of Edwards has been
OL,12,Fremoved in the wake of his offences,
OL,13,Fsaying it was the "right thing to do".
OL,15,FMr Jenkins has become renowned for his
OL,16,Fartwork in the area, including a
OL,17,Ftribute to The Queen and to Wales'
OL,18,Fmining history in Cefneithin.
