OL,6,FWestminster Magistrates' Court heard
OL,7,Fthat Edwards, 62, had been involved in
OL,8,Fan online chat with an adult man on
OL,9,FWhatsApp between December 2020 and
OL,10,FAugust 2021, who sent him 377 sexual
OL,11,Fimages, of which 41 were indecent
OL,12,Fimages of children.
OL,14,FThe bulk of these, 36, were sent
OL,15,Fduring a two-month period.
OL,17,FOn 2 February 2021 the man asked
OL,18,Fwhether what he was sending was too
OL,19,Fyoung, in response to which Edwards
OL,20,Ftold him not to send any underage
OL,21,Fimages.
